column5: Im looking for a good area to camp near ear falls or rainy lake. Any ideas?
Check out Goose Bay Camp. Andrea offers camp sites, they have a shower house available. I have stayed with her many many times! Good luck Will, when you going ?
Where looking for a place hopfully a second trip this year. Still looking for a time. Thanks
Whitewing Resort has a nice camping area with a shower house.www.whitewingresort.com
